    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/bc5c38a57da660f7dd5ca6253fb02803.poster.avif?t=1743082176\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/bc5c38a57da660f7dd5ca6253fb02803.webm?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/bc5c38a57da660f7dd5ca6253fb02803.mp4?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>踏上古埃及的旅程，征服地牢，面对神话中的生物。在你通过每个地牢的过程中建立和完善你的卡组，与老板和敌人对峙。揭开隐藏的宝藏，发现强大的神器、药水和史诗般的卡牌，升级，解锁新的技能和选项，以保护整个埃及!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/08da71d4a15bc146ac074a9a31e7f75f.poster.avif?t=1743082176\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/08da71d4a15bc146ac074a9a31e7f75f.webm?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/08da71d4a15bc146ac074a9a31e7f75f.mp4?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过100张卡牌可用于建立你的卡组<br></li><li>面对10多种类型的敌人。巨人、僵尸、小恶魔和更多。<br></li><li>老板的战斗! 每个地牢你都会遇到一个老板。<br></li><li>升级你的角色，增加HP或能量水平，解锁休息选项，以及在地牢中的更多内容!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/d79b4e385115eae39be29d8b69864d9f.poster.avif?t=1743082176\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/d79b4e385115eae39be29d8b69864d9f.webm?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/d79b4e385115eae39be29d8b69864d9f.mp4?t=1743082176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在神的巢穴中为你的角色解锁明确的升级。<br></li><li>通过选择一套带有随机神器的初始卡牌来开始你的运行。<br></li><li>每场战斗都能解锁新的卡牌和神器，供你在卡组中使用。<br></li><li>打开箱子，找到新的战利品，如神器、药水或史诗卡!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167550/extras/76d10fe18427ec23e20b13f49fcb1737.avif?t=1743082176\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><br>Creeping Deck是Tavrox Games（Overboss，Neurodeck）和Miju Games（Planet crafters）的首次合作，这两个独立游戏工作室源自法国南部的同一个城市，他们联手通过游戏创造具有挑战性和战略性的经验",
